SELECT i_manufact_id, s_zip, ss_net_paid_inc_tax, cd_purchase_estimate, sr_return_ship_cost FROM customer_demographics JOIN store_returns ON sr_cdemo_sk = cd_demo_sk JOIN store ON s_store_sk = sr_store_sk JOIN store_sales ON ss_store_sk = s_store_sk JOIN item ON i_item_sk = ss_item_sk WHERE ss_promo_sk = 185 AND sr_return_time_sk < 38110 AND ss_item_sk <> 4120 AND ss_ext_sales_price <= 373.24

SELECT cs_ext_list_price, cr_returning_addr_sk, c_birth_country, hd_vehicle_count FROM catalog_returns JOIN household_demographics ON hd_demo_sk = cr_returning_hdemo_sk JOIN customer ON c_current_hdemo_sk = hd_demo_sk JOIN catalog_sales ON cs_ship_customer_sk = c_customer_sk WHERE c_first_name <> 'Edwin' AND cr_call_center_sk < 6 AND cs_coupon_amt < 55.86 ORDER BY c_birth_country ASC

SELECT ws_quantity, wr_reason_sk, wp_url FROM web_returns JOIN web_page ON wp_web_page_sk = wr_web_page_sk JOIN web_sales ON ws_web_page_sk = wp_web_page_sk WHERE wr_item_sk > 3100 AND wp_web_page_sk <= 18 AND ws_quantity < 35 ORDER BY ws_quantity DESC

SELECT sr_return_amt_inc_tax, wr_returned_time_sk, ca_address_id, hd_buy_potential, r_reason_id, MAX(r_reason_desc) FROM household_demographics JOIN web_returns ON wr_returning_hdemo_sk = hd_demo_sk JOIN reason ON r_reason_sk = wr_reason_sk JOIN store_returns ON sr_reason_sk = r_reason_sk JOIN customer_address ON ca_address_sk = sr_addr_sk WHERE hd_income_band_sk <= 6 AND wr_web_page_sk >= 54 GROUP BY sr_return_amt_inc_tax, wr_returned_time_sk, ca_address_id, hd_buy_potential, r_reason_id

SELECT sr_addr_sk, ws_list_price, wr_returning_hdemo_sk, wp_web_page_id, sm_ship_mode_sk, r_reason_id FROM store_returns JOIN reason ON r_reason_sk = sr_reason_sk JOIN web_returns ON wr_reason_sk = r_reason_sk JOIN web_page ON wp_web_page_sk = wr_web_page_sk JOIN web_sales ON ws_web_page_sk = wp_web_page_sk JOIN ship_mode ON sm_ship_mode_sk = ws_ship_mode_sk WHERE ws_ext_wholesale_cost = 267.96 AND ws_net_profit <= -122.72

SELECT w_street_name, inv_date_sk FROM warehouse, inventory WHERE w_country > 'United States' AND w_warehouse_sq_ft >= 213141 AND inv_warehouse_sk >= 3 AND w_zip >= '31904' AND w_warehouse_id <> 'AAAAAAAAFAAAAAAA' ORDER BY w_street_name DESC

SELECT wr_fee, inv_item_sk, t_time, i_color, sr_store_sk FROM inventory JOIN item ON i_item_sk = inv_item_sk JOIN web_returns ON wr_item_sk = i_item_sk JOIN time_dim ON t_time_sk = wr_returned_time_sk JOIN store_returns ON sr_return_time_sk = t_time_sk WHERE wr_return_tax <> 129.82 AND wr_reason_sk = 28 ORDER BY inv_item_sk DESC, i_color ASC

SELECT cr_returning_cdemo_sk, ss_ext_wholesale_cost, hd_income_band_sk, MIN(ss_net_paid_inc_tax) FROM store_sales JOIN household_demographics ON hd_demo_sk = ss_hdemo_sk JOIN catalog_returns ON cr_returning_hdemo_sk = hd_demo_sk WHERE hd_vehicle_count >= 0 AND ss_sold_date_sk < 2452160 GROUP BY cr_returning_cdemo_sk, ss_ext_wholesale_cost, hd_income_band_sk HAVING MIN(ss_net_paid_inc_tax) >= 519.49 ORDER BY MIN(ss_net_paid_inc_tax) ASC

SELECT cp_catalog_page_id, p_item_sk, cs_catalog_page_sk, cr_ship_mode_sk, cd_dep_employed_count FROM customer_demographics JOIN catalog_returns ON cr_returning_cdemo_sk = cd_demo_sk JOIN catalog_page ON cp_catalog_page_sk = cr_catalog_page_sk JOIN catalog_sales ON cs_catalog_page_sk = cp_catalog_page_sk JOIN promotion ON p_promo_sk = cs_promo_sk WHERE cp_type > 'monthly' AND p_channel_catalog = 'N' ORDER BY cd_dep_employed_count ASC, cp_catalog_page_id DESC, cs_catalog_page_sk ASC

SELECT ws_ext_tax, cr_net_loss, cd_demo_sk, ca_city, COUNT(ws_ext_discount_amt) FROM customer_demographics JOIN web_sales ON ws_ship_cdemo_sk = cd_demo_sk JOIN customer_address ON ca_address_sk = ws_ship_addr_sk JOIN catalog_returns ON cr_returning_addr_sk = ca_address_sk WHERE cr_reason_sk <= 27 AND ca_street_number <= '789' GROUP BY ws_ext_tax, cr_net_loss, cd_demo_sk, ca_city ORDER BY COUNT(ws_ext_discount_amt) ASC

SELECT i_category, c_salutation, cs_coupon_amt, w_zip, cr_return_tax, ws_quantity FROM warehouse JOIN catalog_returns ON cr_warehouse_sk = w_warehouse_sk JOIN customer ON c_customer_sk = cr_returning_customer_sk JOIN catalog_sales ON cs_ship_customer_sk = c_customer_sk JOIN item ON i_item_sk = cs_item_sk JOIN web_sales ON ws_item_sk = i_item_sk WHERE i_product_name > 'callyeingableese' AND cr_call_center_sk < 6 ORDER BY cr_return_tax DESC
